# Agent Checklist

**Before responding to user, verify:**

## Git

- [ ] On feature branch (not main)
- [ ] Atomic commits with conventional prefixes (feat/fix/refactor/docs/chore)
- [ ] Branch merged to main when complete
- [ ] Feature branch deleted

## Docs

